Output docs/kubeagent-demo.gif
Require kubeagent
Set Shell bash
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1120
Set Height 940
Set Padding 26
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 55ms

Hide
Type "export PS1='\e[38;5;114m$\e[0m '" Enter
Type "clear" Enter
Show
Sleep 800ms
Type "kubeagent scan"
Sleep 700ms
Enter
Sleep 6500ms
